18th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 14 Highlights

Stage 14 is another hilly one starting in Rodez and travelling 178km to the finish in Mende, up the cat two Cote de la Croix Neuve at a 10 per cent gradient. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
